      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Mint-condition vehicle that shows exceptionally well inside and out. The exterior is very clean with a sharp, well-kept appearance, and the interior is equally impressive with minimal visible wear. This is the kind of used car that feels clearly cared for, with a strong overall presentation and no notable cosmetic issues beyond the light signs of normal use you might expect on a pre-owned vehicle. A buyer should expect a very clean, standout example that\u2019s ready to enjoy.",
