      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward, affordable transportation for the buyer who values practicality and opportunity. It presents as a sensible budget option with plenty of usable life for commuting, errands, or a starter vehicle. An honest offering with clear value, this is a chance to get into a dependable car at an accessible price point.",
