      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants affordable wheels, a practical project, or a handy spare car. Easy to like, straightforward, and priced to make sense \u2014 if you\u2019re after cheap motoring with character, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or backup driver with strong value for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. The engine starts up and runs, the drivetrain pulls the car through the gears, and the chassis still feels like a usable platform with plenty of life for the right owner. Cosmetic wear, age-related flaws, and needed attention are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. Good candidate for a hands-on buyer seeking inexpensive transportation, a parts donor, or a straightforward restoration base.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap way into a car. Runs, drives, and gets the job done. Not pretty. Priced to move fast. Solid project or beater.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of worn-in character you can't fake\u2014a true underdog with presence, personality, and plenty of story left to write. It's the sort of ride that speaks to someone who sees potential instead of polish: a perfect canvas for a hands-on project, a budget-friendly runabout, or a bold base for a custom vision. If you\u2019ve been looking for something inexpensive with undeniable spirit, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel of something memorable without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
